{"tid":1855634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子於網傳政府口罩倉庫樓下徘徊被捕","createTime":"2020-02-01T07:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T17:02:38.000Z","uid":48093,"like":82,"dislike":364,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"b3bf3c4f675cf19b69a0a939ea014c2d9f8426c6","tid":1855634,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:46:46.000Z","msg":"近日網上有人公開政府存放口罩的倉庫地址，警方昨日在其中一個倉庫樓下發現一名男子形跡可疑，以遊蕩罪拘捕他。被捕人士是報稱倉務員的21歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n葵青區刑事調查隊第三隊督察方綺蓓表示，疑犯在政府存放口罩的工廠大廈下徘徊，被截查後未能提出在該處逗留的原因，懷疑他有機會犯案。她又稱，當時疑犯身上沒有武器或可作非法用途的工具。<br />\n<br />\n方綺蓓說，警方高度關注意圖製造社會恐慌的網上謠言，強烈譴責煽惑他人干犯刑事罪行的行為，呼籲市民小心求證傳言，不要誤信謠言。"},{"pid":"96f8b92cfcb6352db207142bab9dac2ca134a9da","tid":1855634,"uid":79793,"like":315,"dislike":5,"score":310,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"做倉係倉附近行比狗拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152e9dd6e6b710b2cb54b07e59f94e4bd8ccca78","tid":1855634,"uid":46042,"like":381,"dislike":3,"score":378,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"行過都拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />癲過北韓"},{"pid":"eefe3527dbc11b93374d87f5d7686c3d1b37de8c","tid":1855634,"uid":138868,"like":423,"dislike":0,"score":423,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"啫係個倉係真"},{"pid":"8ebad37dcf95998a8f6c6a86dd4ca14c85465ddb","tid":1855634,"uid":51271,"like":183,"dislike":0,"score":183,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"當時疑犯身上沒有武器或可作非法用途的工具<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鳩拉到呢"},{"pid":"d276a56ce0c34c73353a381287c39da97dbbdae8","tid":1855634,"uid":76591,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"行過都拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc3f42bfa781655b6e08daf181f1d34f51c4e37","tid":1855634,"uid":63838,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":4,"r